00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:42.720
director of the secret service, in his office&nbsp;
- General Vladimir Korchnoi is there as well.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:43.360 --> 00:01:47.600
They show Ivan a video of Nate's meeting at the&nbsp;
park and mention he's a CIA agent that left the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:52.000
country that morning, but their main interest lies&nbsp;
in the other man and finding out his identity.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:56.240
We cut to Dominika then, who is waking up at&nbsp;
the hospital to find her leg in a metal frame,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:59.120
she starts crying when she realizes&nbsp;
she won't be able to dance again.&nbsp;

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:03.920
Three months pass. Dominika, who is&nbsp;
still walking with the aid of a cane,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:08.320
is visited by Ivan. He comments on the fact&nbsp;
a replacement for her has already been found&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:08.320 --> 00:02:12.160
