plus a recording of a conversation between&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:32.240
them that implies he jumped on her on purpose&nbsp;
so his girlfriend could take Dominika's place.&nbsp;

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:36.560
Later that day, we find Dominika in the&nbsp;
theatre, watching her former partner and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:41.360
the new girl practice. After they're done, they&nbsp;
