the hotel Ustinov is staying in,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:30.800 --> 00:03:35.360
wearing the dress she's been given. She goes to&nbsp;
the bar to wait for Ustinov to approach her first,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:39.760
which he does. Dominika tells him she's come&nbsp;
