to her place to wait for his signal, which is a&nbsp;
simple phone call that plays her favorite song.&nbsp;

00:12:18.400 --> 00:12:22.560
Dominika meets with Nate's superiors and is put&nbsp;
through a liar detector test to see if she can be&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:22.560 --> 00:12:27.600
trusted. When they accept her, she asks for money.&nbsp;
They laugh at her, but they change their minds&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:32.000
when she tells them she can give them Boucher. The&nbsp;
following Friday, the whole team flies to London&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:32.000 --> 00:12:37.200
to meet with Boucher. Dominika stays in a special&nbsp;
hotel room the CIA prepared for her with security&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:41.680
cameras to monitor her and a set of disks hidden&nbsp;
under a desk to change for the real ones later.&nbsp;

00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:46.080
Moments later, while she's at the bar waiting for&nbsp;
Boucher, he's surprised by the sudden appearance&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:46.080 --> 00:12:50.480
of Volontov who supposedly wants to help.&nbsp;
Dominika sends him to her room, otherwise&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:55.040
his presence will scare Boucher off. Boucher&nbsp;
arrives soon afterward and Dominika goes to her,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:55.040 --> 00:12:59.520
explaining Marta sent her. Boucher doesn't like&nbsp;
this change and is about to leave, but Dominika&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:59.520 --> 00:13:03.760
convinces her to stay when she threatens her with&nbsp;
some dangerous pictures and mentions the money.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:08.480
Both women go to Dominika's room where Volontov is&nbsp;
waiting. Boucher gives her the disks in exchange&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:08.480 --> 00:13:12.560
for the money, and Dominika pretends to take the&nbsp;
disks to her computer to check they're real when&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:17.040
she's actually trading them with the CIA's.&nbsp;
Dominika and Volontov leave then after telling&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:21.680
Boucher to wait an hour to leave too, but Boucher&nbsp;
is anxious and drunk so she leaves soon after.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:25.760
When she makes it to the street, she notices&nbsp;
she's being followed and gets scared, so she&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:30.320
throws the money in a trashcan and crosses the&nbsp;
street where a truck hits and kills her. Dominika&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:30.320 --> 00:13:34.800
is in a car with Volontov when this happens, and&nbsp;
he quickly gets the news on the phone. He tells&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:34.800 --> 00:13:38.640
Dominika they've been given orders to return&nbsp;
to Moscow immediately and takes her passport.&nbsp;

00:13:39.200 --> 00:13:43.760
When they make it to Moscow, Ivan takes the&nbsp;
disks from Volontov before arresting him.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:48.480
Both he and Dominika are under suspicion of&nbsp;
having helped the Americans. When asked about it,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:52.240
she denies it, so she starts being tortured&nbsp;
in different ways for the real answer,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:56.800
but she doesn't give in. They even show her&nbsp;
a video of how Volontov was shot for lying,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:56.800 --> 00:14:00.240
but when the interrogator points at her&nbsp;
head and she lies again, nothing happens.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:00.800 --> 00:14:05.600
Ivan takes over then, and Dominika manages to&nbsp;
manipulate him into protecting her. She's allowed&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:09.520
to return home, but when she gets there, she&nbsp;
feels so dirty she doesn't let her mom hug her.&nbsp;

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:14.240
After a difficult meeting with Korchnoi and&nbsp;
Zakharov, Ivan returns to his apartment,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:18.160
where Dominika is waiting. He tells her&nbsp;
they've granted her request to let her keep&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:18.160 --> 00:14:23.600
working on Nate, she kisses him before leaving.
Dominika returns to Budapest and meets with Nate.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:23.600 --> 00:14:27.520
They go to his apartment, where he expresses&nbsp;
his suspicions of her quick release.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:27.520 --> 00:14:32.160
Dominika convinces him to relocate her and her mom&nbsp;
to America and to give her more money, he accepts&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:36.640
before they make love. In the middle of the&nbsp;
night, Dominika wakes up when she hears a noise,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:36.640 --> 00:14:41.200
she goes to the kitchen to find Sergei torturing&nbsp;
Nate. She pretends to be on his side at first,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:41.200 --> 00:14:45.360
even helping him hurt Nate to get the name&nbsp;
of the mole. But when Sergei gets distracted,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:49.680
she hits him back and helps Nate cut the straps&nbsp;
tying him to the chair. The three of them get into&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:53.760
a fight that doesn't last long: Sergei slips&nbsp;
and Dominika takes the chance to stab him.&nbsp;

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:58.160
She wakes up in the hospital the next&nbsp;
day, and leaves her room to have a smoke.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:01.520
She's then approached by Korchnoi,&nbsp;
who reveals himself as Marble.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:01.520 --> 00:15:06.000
He thinks he'll be caught soon and doesn't want to&nbsp;
die in vain, so he asks Dominika to expose him so&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:06.000 --> 00:15:10.880
she can become a national hero and take his place&nbsp;
as a mole. She doesn't give him a definite answer,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:10.880 --> 00:15:15.760
but after he leaves, she checks on Nate and leaves&nbsp;
as well. She gives herself up to the police and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:15.760 --> 00:15:20.000
asks to see the Russian ambassador, when she's&nbsp;
taken to him, she tells him to call Zakharov and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:23.440
inform him she has the name of the mole, which&nbsp;
she'll give him in exchange for her freedom.&nbsp;

00:15:24.080 --> 00:15:28.320
A meeting to do the exchange is arranged later&nbsp;
that night at an airport. Nate will walk with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:32.720
her to confirm the identity of the mole and she&nbsp;
mustn't try to run or she'll be shot. Nate is&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:36.880
angry with her because he thinks she's used him,&nbsp;
but she has a surprise: when the Russians approach&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:36.880 --> 00:15:41.680
them with the mole, they take the bag off his face&nbsp;
to reveal it's not Korchnoi - it's her uncle Ivan,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:41.680 --> 00:15:46.000
who has been framed thanks to Dominika fabricating&nbsp;
evidence since she made it to Budapest the first&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:51.200
time. Nate quickly catches on and confirms&nbsp;
Ivan is the mole. After the exchange is done,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:51.200 --> 00:15:54.960
Ivan is shot by a Russian sniper and&nbsp;
Dominika is taken away on a helicopter.&nbsp;

00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:59.600
Back in Russia, she's named a heroine and&nbsp;
allowed to have a good life with her mom.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:59.600 --> 00:16:03.600
The movie ends when she receives a phone call and&nbsp;
the only sound on the line is her favorite song.

